  <brief_title>Ropivacaine Hypobaric Spinal Anaesthesia in Traumatic Hip Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Determining the Minimum Effective Ropivacaine Dose for Unilateral Hypobaric Spinal Anaesthesia During Traumatic Femoral Neck Surgery in the Aged Person: Prospective Comparative Randomized Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
